com.oracle.bmc

Enum Region

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<Region>
      • com.oracle.bmc.Region
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<Region>

    public enum Region
extends Enum<Region>

    Enumeration of all of the known Regions that can be contacted.

    Note, not all services may be available in all regions.
